Package dalserver.sia

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SiapKeywordFactory
    SiapKeywordFactory implements a factory class for well-known SIAP keywords, including Groups, Params and Fields.
    SiapMySql
    SiapMySql provides a simple image access (SIAP Version 2) capability for any image collection which can be described via image metadata stored in a MySQL database.
    SiapOracle
    SiapOracle provides a simple image access (SIAP Version 2) capability for any image collection which can be described via image metadata stored in an Oracle database.
    SiapParamSet
    Construct an initial default parameter set containing the parameters for a SIAP service.
    SiapQuery
    SiapQuery provides a simple image access capability for any image collection which can be described via image metadata stored in a DBMS-hosted Image table.
    SiapService
    This generic class implements the service operations for a DALServer SIAP service, independent of the transport protocol (HTTP).
    SiapServlet
    Generic HTTP Servlet for the Simple Image Access (SIA) protocol.
    SiapTestQuery
    SiapTestQuery simulates a SIA database query class, implementing the null query, which returns only standard SIA / ImageDM metadata.
    SiapV1KeywordData
    Raw data for the SIAP and Image data models (this class is autogenerated).
    SiapV2KeywordData
    Raw data for the SIAP and Image data models (this class is autogenerated).
